  • 【Touch & Voice-Assistant Control】 HD hands free calling and listen to music. The smart glasses can easily call Smart Phone Assistant, and connect to your favorite music stations. Click to play or pause songs, answer calls.
  • 【Open Ear Smart Glasses】 Enjoy an open-ear sound experience with our Bluetooth glasses, allowing you to stay fully aware of your surroundings while still listening to your favorite audio.
  • 【Advanced Bluetooth 5.3 Technology】Featuring the latest Bluetooth 5.3 chip for stable connection, fast transmission, and strong compatibility. Supports voice assistant for convenient smart operation
  • 【Highly efficient anti-blue light lenses】effectively filter harmful bluelight, protect your eyes, and reduce eye fatigue caused by prolonged use of electronic devices
  • 【LONG LASTING BATTERY】 Powered by a built in 160mAh lithium ion battery, it offers up to 4 hours of playtime and 5 hours of call time, and 100 hours of standby time with just 1.5‑2 hours of charging.
